类 CountEvictor<W extends Window>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.windowing.evictors.CountEvictor<W>
  • 类型参数:
    W - The type of Windows on which this Evictor can operate.

public class CountEvictor<W extends Window>
extends Object

    An Evictor that keeps up to a certain amount of elements.

    • 方法详细资料

      • evict

        public int evict(Iterable<StreamRecord<Object>> elements,
                 int size,
                 W window)
        从接口复制的说明: Evictor
        Computes how many elements should be removed from the pane. The result specifies how many elements should be removed from the beginning.
        指定者:
        evict 在接口中 Evictor<Object,W extends Window>
        参数:
        elements - The elements currently in the pane.
        size - The current number of elements in the pane.
        window - The Window

      • of

        public static <W extends Window> CountEvictor<W> of(long maxCount)
        Creates a CountEvictor that keeps the given number of elements.
        参数:
        maxCount - The number of elements to keep in the pane.
